column38:
I used pretrained BERT models from HuggingFace:
- "ixa-ehu/berteus-base-cased" for back-translation with the BERT-fused NMT.
- "adamlin/NCBI_BERT_pubmed_mimic_uncased_base_transformers" for the translations with the BERT-fused NMT.

column15: We used HuggingFace implementation with changes in Tokenizer and postprocessing. We added special latin tokens to tokenizer since it was not able to deal with latin words as a with a tilde. We also added the most common portuguese word found (best result for previous tests was adding just one word + special tokens).
